      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been a dream. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape\u2014super clean, runs like a champ, and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to go with zero stress. I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
