    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The 3.2L atmospheric inline-six pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline, benefiting from a recent VANOS overhaul and valve adjustment. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement, ensuring the integrity of the multi-link rear suspension under load. While the exterior shows minor road rash consistent with spirited use, the bushings are tight and the dampers remain responsive. A high-engagement driver's car that prioritizes mechanical excellence.",
      "price": 36500.0,
