    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility. The exterior finish maintains a high-gloss shine, with only minor, superficial stone chips on the front fascia that are consistent with light highway use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is free of tears or significant bolster wear, and the interior has never been smoked in. All electronic features, from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, operate exactly as they should. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and the transmission shifts with precision. I have adhered to a strict maintenance schedule, and a comprehensive folder of service receipts will be provided to the new owner. It has recently undergone a full fluid service and a multi-point safety inspection, ensuring it is ready for the road from day one. This is a dependable, honest car for a buyer who values consistent upkeep and a clean history.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
