      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, which demonstrates a commitment to mechanical excellence and aesthetic preservation. Rigorously inspected to ensure operational integrity, this model offers a dependable and refined driving experience. The interior remains in superior condition, complemented by an exterior that reflects diligent care. This offering represents a premier opportunity for the professional buyer seeking a balance of performance and long-term value.",
      "price": 34500.0,
