    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been truly cared for? I\u2019m parting with my car, and it\u2019s in wonderful shape! It\u2019s been a fantastic companion on the road, running smoothly and looking great. I\u2019ve kept up with the maintenance, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next owner today. It\u2019s the perfect balance of quality and value\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 33500.0,
