    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is managed through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis dynamics are preserved with recent subframe reinforcement and refreshed suspension bushings, ensuring precise turn-in and neutral handling characteristics. Mechanical upkeep is current, including a comprehensive VANOS service and valve clearance adjustment. While the exterior shows honest patina from spirited use, the drivetrain remains robust and the linear power delivery is as visceral as the day it left Regensburg.",
